lliurex-auto-upgrade (0.28.0) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Moved service to notify. Notifies steps to systemd  
  * Inhibits shutdown when installing packages
  * Checks if dpkg is being executed before entering a loop
  * Inotify to check if a new tag has been written. Disabled by default for
    now.
  * Outputs which packages are going to be installed.
  * systemd status now shows what lliurex-auto-upgrade is doing

